so here is my workflow

1) git config sendemail.to foo@bar.com (m8r's email). this is required only once

2) git format-patch. edit Cc and add In-Reply-To:

3) run git-send-email --envelope-sender "Miklos Vajna <vmiklos@frugalware.org>" --from "Miklos Vajna <vmiklos@frugalware.org>" *.patch

i'm still wondering if this is the perfect workflow, but i'm pretty sure it is
